{"word":"ἀπέχω","slug":"ἀπέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀπέχω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔχω\">ἔχω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> in commercial sense ‘acknowledge receipt’, <b><i>have in full, have received</i> <a href='B:470 6:2'>Mt 6:2</a>; <a href='B:480 14:41'>Mk 14:41</a></b> (if Judas is the subject; for impersonal sense see 4 below); <b><a href='B:490 6:24'>Lk 6:24</a>; <a href='B:570 4:18'>Phil 4:18</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <i>have back</i> <b><a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 15</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b><i>be away from</i> <a href='B:470 14:24'>Mt 14:24</a>; <a href='B:490 7:6'>Lk 7:6</a>; <i>be distant</i> <a href='B:490 24:13'>24:13</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> ‘hold oneself off from, avoid contact with’, with <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><i>abstain from</i><a href='B:510 15:20'>Ac 15:20</a>, <a href='B:510 15:29'>29</a>; <a href='B:590 4:3'>1 Th 4:3</a>; <a href='B:610 4:3'>1 Ti 4:3</a>; <a href='B:670 2:11'>1 Pt 2:11</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>4.</pp></b> the rendering <b><i>it is enough</i> <a href='B:480 14:41'>Mk 14:41</a></b> enjoys strong support, but see 1. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπεστράφην\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπηγγέλην\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}